title: Kubernetes namespaces
agents: linux
author: Henri Wahl <henri@nagstamon.de>
catalog: generic
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the status of Kubernetes namespaces.
 You need to install the plugin {kubernetes_namespaces}
 into the {plugins} directory of your agent.

 The check monitors namespace status and resources.

inventory:
 One service will be created for each Kubernetes namespace
 where the {kubernetes_namespaces} plugin produces a non-empty output.

